.000Z","msg":"話比身邊人知拖越耐越不利<br />\n示威者都會累<br />\n政府會有更多時間計劃同操作各方面牽制示威<br />\n絕不能比政府拖延<br />\n要設時限升級施壓，保持令國際新聞關注<br />\n香港輸左就玩完<br />\n絕對唔可以讓步/階段性勝利<br />\n目標只有「撤回」<br />\n今次唔贏以後我地示威抗爭政府都唔會再怕！<br />\n警察同政府而家係重複緊雨傘時既戰略<br />\n香港人要開始轉變<br />\n和理非+適當既勇武配合我地先有一線機會<br />\n雨傘衰過一次<br />\n預演又錯過一次時機<br />\n唔好再重複犯錯，會斷送成個香港後悔一世<br />\n加油呀香港人！"},{"pid":"003957cdef86d74ef2065855f510be2c0f50f322","tid":1206160,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"有啊<br />\n今朝落大雨,好多地盤都順便罷左工"},{"pid":"56348be377dd33d47a10a00314d5544e93a57014","tid":1206160,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ef8132d09d9945c0713e031757fc718bc13f6d","tid":1206160,"uid":244802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00cb290137e8c67a9b8916bea98761683f3e9161","tid":1206160,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:15:22.000Z","msg":"因為地盤佬手停口停 點會彩你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:33:43.000Z","msg":"湊完女，出緊去撐場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4264a40683d810dfacf85af425abe77fe6e2854b","tid":1206160,"uid":40287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:34:43.000Z","msg":"&lt;一  地盤佬，全公司得我一個罷工。"},{"pid":"97544d231e09812751681edd1941d83b019d38f8","tid":1206160,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:34:56.000Z","msg":"聽朋友話佢間建築公司今日要點人名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6628582e38aa4f67e5986d410047bdddc6db87d4","tid":1206160,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1576a24f3b18592f86e75f3d66b86c954e92719f","tid":1206160,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:55:48.000Z","msg":"冇事就屌地盤佬<br />\n有事就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=